---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageTitle from '../components/PageTitle.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Shipping & Returns | Peptide Shop"
  breadcrumbs={[
    { name: "Home", url: "/" },
    { name: "Shipping & Returns", url: "/shipping" }
  ]}
>
  <PageTitle 
    title="Shipping & Returns"
    subtitle="Fast UK delivery with discreet packaging. Free shipping on orders over Â£500."
    breadcrumbs={[
      { name: "Home", url: "/" },
      { name: "Shipping & Returns" }
    ]}
  />

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-10">
          <h2 class="mb-3">Shipping Policy</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">We ship to most countries within the European Union. All orders are dispatched from our EU warehouse.</p>
          <ul class="list-unstyled mb-5">
            <li class="mb-2 d-flex align-items-start"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="mr-2 mt-1 text-color flex-shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg><span><strong>Processing Time:</strong> Orders are typically processed within 1-2 business days.</span></li>
            <li class="mb-2 d-flex align-items-start"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="mr-2 mt-1 text-color flex-shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg><span><strong>Shipping Method:</strong> We use express couriers (DHL, FedEx, Royal Mail) for all shipments.</span></li>
            <li class="mb-2 d-flex align-items-start"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="mr-2 mt-1 text-color flex-shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg><span><strong>Temperature Control:</strong> 
              <ul class="list-unstyled ml-4 mt-2">
                <li class="mb-1 d-flex align-items-start"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="mr-2 mt-1 text-color flex-shrink-0"><path d="m9 18 6-6-6-6"/></svg><span><strong>Research Peptides:</strong> Lyophilized peptides are stable at ambient temperatures during transit.</span></li>
                <li class="mb-1 d-flex align-items-start"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="mr-2 mt-1 text-color flex-shrink-0"><path d="m9 18 6-6-6-6"/></svg><span><strong>Skincare & Wellness:</strong> Most products are stable at room temperature. Temperature-sensitive items are shipped with cold packs.</span></li>
              </ul>
            </span></li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="mb-3">Return Policy</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">Due to the nature of our products, we have specific return policies for each category:</p>
          
          <h3 class="h5 mb-3">Research Peptides</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">We generally do not accept returns of research chemicals to ensure the integrity of our supply chain. Once a product leaves our facility, we cannot guarantee its storage conditions.</p>

          <h3 class="h5 mb-3">Skincare & Wellness</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">Unopened skincare and wellness products may be returned within 14 days of delivery. Please contact support to initiate a return. Opened products cannot be returned for hygiene reasons.</p>

          <div class="alert alert-info border-0 shadow-sm d-flex align-items-start" role="alert">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="mr-2 mt-1 flex-shrink-0"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><line x1="12" x2="12" y1="16" y2="12"></line><line x1="12" x2="12.01" y1="8" y2="8"></line></svg>
            <span>If you receive a damaged item or an incorrect product, please contact us within 48 hours of receipt, and we will arrange for a replacement.</span>
          </div>

          <h2 class="mt-5 mb-3">Customs & Import Duties</h2>
          <p>For orders within the EU, there are no customs duties. For international orders, the customer is responsible for any import duties, taxes, or clearance fees.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
